originalText.text: This is the second time I come here for treatment. The first time was for severe lower back pain in 2016 and I recovered fully. Now for my sciatica pain I have come back and I’m getting better as I go! The staff here is wonderful!! From Gina the receptionist, Sam, the current acupuncturist to Dr. K!! They are all very nice, polite and professional. They saved my back before And I’m positive they will do so again now! Thank you guys!! I highly recommend them!!

originalText.text:
I went to a chiropractor / physical therapist before about a year ago just for general back pain and although he was nice I wasn't getting the results I had hoped for and stopped seeing him. So many of my coworkers recommended this place to me after I had a recent injury on the job and I am so happy I took their advice. After only 3 visits, Dr. Kazhdan has already helped me identify a lot of the pain and had me get x rays done to develop a treatment plan. He's helping me find stretches / small exercises for me and I'm already feeling progress. I love how he explains things and answers the questions I have without making me feel dumb for not knowing what could seem obvious. I look forward to a pain free spine down the road!

Not to forget how lovely Gina and Kathy have always been at the front desk. This is the kind of customer service that should never be overlooked. There are so many negative reviews insulting customer service workers / receptionists / people who work with people doing the best they can, and we often forget to give them the praise they deserve. Working with the public on a daily basis myself, I notice it, I see it, and I appreciate it.

Thank you, Manhattan Wellness, for going above and beyond my expectations and, in the middle of a world on fire, making your clients feel at ease and welcome. We need more kindness these days, especially. I am so lucky to have found a provider that quite literally does "have my back." Highly, highly recommend. :)

originalText.text: I love Manhattan Wellness group! I started going because I bought a groupon for acupuncture and cupping and I had no idea I would fall in love with this place and be coming every 2 weeks for treatments! Dr Trabulsi is an amazing chiropractor and really cares about his patients. James is the best as well! Highly recommend any treatment here!!
